Gary Watts wrote:

> Can shocks be changed without having a lift to get all the wheels off 
> at once.  

I replaced mine without lifting the bus at all.  i wouldn't want it on a 
jack stand or the like as it took quite a bit of beating and pounding 
and heat and cold chisel to get them of the torsion bars.   It was more 
work that I thought it would be.  A picture is worth a thousand words...

http://dev.radom.org/v/vw/projects/shocks/

